data.description: This spacious and open end-unit home will impress with its finishes and overall condition. This 2020 built home still looks and feels new. The kitchen features an abundance of cabinets, granite countertops, huge island that opens to the family room and stainless steel appliances including a gas range. The upper level boasts three bedrooms, two bathrooms and a nook - perfect for a desk. The large primary bedroom won't disappoint with a 3/4 bathroom complete with dual sinks, granite countertops, sizable walk-in shower and huge closet. Great location adjacent to open space. Amazing opportunity. Turnkey home. All appliances are included. Must see!
